According to [Notification] by Lianjiang Police(https://weibo.com/1974576991/N9bX0ql1c?refer_flag=1001030103_)The attack occurred around 7.40 am. Lianjiang is a city with a population of less than 2 million. It is about 500 kilometers west of Shenzhen. A 25 -year -old man named Wu has been arrested. The notification did not indicate the possible motivation to commit crimes.

