![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T04-41-00-04-00/000000.png)The Social Work Department of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China recently exposed and put into operation in official media [![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T04-41-00-04-00/000001.png)](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/gt2-07102023044035.html/@@images/image)Associated Press Information Picture [Audio-Link: https: //www.rfa.org/mandarin/yatabaODao/Zhengzhi/GT2-07102023044035.html/@stream](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/gt2-07102023044035.html/@@stream)The Social Work Department of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China has recently exposed and put into operation in official media; however, the official has not disclosed its internal structure. Scholars believe that the Ministry of Industry of the Central News Agency continued the functions of Mao Zedong's establishment of the Central Social Ministry of the Central Committee in Yan'an in 1941, and his work covered the grass -roots government.

[** Chinese institutional reform plan exposes weakness experts: strengthen centralization **](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/jw-03162023094829.html)*[** The important institutions of the State Council are placed in the era of the Communist Party of China, the senior management of the Communist Party of China is about to enter the era of strong party and weak politics **](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/gt1-02272023002307.html)According to the "Rule of Law Daily" report, Wu Han Sheng, Minister of Social Work of the Central Committee, hosted a special seminar on the letter and visits of provincial and ministerial cadres on Friday (7th). This is the first time that Chinese official media has disclosed the news that Wu Hansheng has served as the Minister of Social Work of the Central Committee.

According to the official website of the China Quality Association on Monday, Liu Zheng presided over the first batch of National Industry Association Chamber of Commerce and Chamber of Commerce's theme education research seminar on July 6 as the deputy minister of the Central Social Work Department. People noticed that the two ministerial officials appeared in the way of attending the meeting, not officially officially reported.

Ding Hanqiang, a scholar who lives in Australia, said in an interview on Monday this Monday that the newly formed "Ministry of Social Work of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China" was called "the CPC Central Committee" during the Yan'an period. The Central Social Work Department is intended to strengthen internal control. He said: "In order to consolidate the regime, the Social Work Department is the penetration and control of all aspects. It can be said that in addition to the network management and network supervision, it is to strengthen the social work department, which is nothing more than maintaining stability."

** Eighty years ago, Mao Zedong formed the Central Social Department **

Before the establishment of the Communist Party of China in 1939, Mao Zedong established the Social Department and the Central Intelligence Department of the Central Committee of the Communist Party of China in Yan'an. Kang Sheng served as Minister and Leading Intelligence (Anti -Spy). Since then, Mao Zedong launched the Yan'an rectification movement, and tens of thousands of cadres were beaten into agents, traitors and traitors. The so -called criminal evidence was fabricated by the Central Social Ministry. The department was dissolved in 1949.

![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T04-41-00-04-00/000002.png)Minister of Social Work, Wu Hansheng, recently appeared publicly. (Network data map) [![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T04-41-00-04-00/000003.png)](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/zhengzhi/gt2-07102023044035.html/image.png)In an interview with current affairs commentators, Cai Shenkun said that it shows that above, the Central Social Work Department uniformly leads the State Letters and Calls Bureau to guide the party building of mixed -owned enterprises, non -public ownership enterprises and new economic organizations, social organizations, and employment groups. But the fact is not so simple. He said: "In fact, this department is not simple, it penetrates every corner of society. In these years, they have discovered that ordinary people are a big problem. He does not know what the people are thinking and what to do. After the establishment of this department , Find more enemies in the whole society, differentiate the enemy, and disintegrate the enemy. "

In mid -March this year, China officially announced the reform plan of the CPC Central Committee's institutional institution, set up a new Central Social Work Department, and is responsible for overall guidance of letters and visits. Officials say that the Central Social Work Department formulates responsibilities such as social work policies, and coordinated the promotion of party building to lead grass -roots governance and grass -roots regime construction. It also said that the provincial, municipal, and county -level party committees set up social work departments to be corresponding to the responsibilities of the "two new" workers' committees of party committees and organizations at the same level.

** The functions of the Social Work Department are extensive and penetrated into the grass -roots government **

In other words, the grass -roots organizations of the Central Social Work Department have penetrated into the first -level party branch of local townships and towns without being subject to the administrative department of the State Council. Cai Shenkun continued: "In the past, many of our letters and visits belonged to the national administrative level and government level, but now the Central Social Work Department has been improved to the CCP level, and this institution is with the Central Organization Department, the Central Propaganda Department, the Central United Front of the Central Committee, the Central United Front of the Central Committee. The Ministry of Political and Legal Committee is on the same place. I believe that the Minister of the Central Social Work Department will enter the Politburo in the future. "

Cai Shenkun believes that the Central Social Work Department will enter the grass -roots party committee: "His hand reached to each grass -roots government without dead ends. Including all civil organizations, social organizations, and all chambers of commerce."

Wang Jian, a media person, said that the newly established Central Social Work Department belongs to the super institution. Public security, Guoan, anti -terrorism, transportation, immigration, and even social organizations under the jurisdiction of the Ministry of Civil Affairs can be understood as concentrations of the CCP's Internal Affairs Commission (unprepared) concentrated) Version.

