*** ["Complete" Hong Kong Legislative Council election has only eight claims to be nominated for non -pro -Beijing candidates](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ac-11102021073248.html)** *** [Hong Kong Parliament to realize the Chinese model efficiency of the Legislative Council boast is the "Ximin Temple" conference](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/ac2-10282021085333.html)***[** Hong Kong "Red Parliament" as a former member of the overseas co -deployment to refuse to recognize **](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/al-01072022130955.html)More than 20 democrats who were promoted to the Hong Kong District Council in 2019 through direct elections have recently seized letters and requested that the international community no longer recognize the parliament of Hong Kong at all levels and no longer recognize the legitimate representative of these parliaments.

The Hong Kong District Council has been generated from almost completely directly in the past, and has evolved to only 20 % of the next seats in the next district council. Of the 470 seats, 179 seats were appointed by the Chief Executive and added 176 seats generated by regional extermination, fire prevention, and district committees.

Candidates must be nominated for three members of the three types of regional committees, and the nominations of 50 constituency voters are added, and they must be confirmed by the District Council Qualification Review Committee of the Chairman of the President of the Administration Affairs Department.

The co -deployment was initiated by Ye Jinlong, a former member of Hong Kong in Japan. He said that the district council constituted a significant modification, marking the official death of the Hong Kong Democratic Parliament system.

Ye Jinlong: "Under the so -called" Patriot Governing Hong Kong "in the Hong Kong Government, if you go to the election, you must express loyalty to the CCP. When they go to these pro -government people to nominate, they represent them to run for the election. Enter the system, make sacrifices, and make actions that violate democratic value. "

![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T11-07-00-04-00/000002.png)Ye Jinlong, a former member of Hong Kong, initiated a joint department, requiring governments to no longer recognize the legitimacy of the Hong Kong Parliament. (Ye Jinlong is exclusively provided, the shooting date is unknown) [![](Images/rfamandarin/2023-07-10T11-07-00-04-00/000003.png)](https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/gangtai/gf-07102023074030.html/m0710gf-1.jpg)** Xu Zhifeng, who was wanted by the Hong Kong Police, participated in the joint departure **

The former Hong Kong District Councilor participating in the co -signed includes Xu Zhifeng, who was wanted by the Hong Kong police. Ye Jinlong believes that they are real public opinion representatives and help strengthen the persuasiveness of the joint departure.

Ye Jinlong: "We are the district councilors selected through the last democratic process. Even if we cannot pass the government's review because of the pressure of the government, we still exist in public opinion. All parts of the world, but the hearts of Hong Kong people are still unchanged. "

Guo Zijian, a former member of Hong Kong, exiled in the UK, also agreed that the current parliament of Hong Kong is just as false.

Guo Zijian: "In addition to the high threshold, you have to get nominations and pass qualification review and political review. Especially for our democratic candidates, it is not easy to pass (threshold). (Hong Kong Government) motivation is obviously obvious It is the principle of hanging the "Patriot Governance Hong Kong" to eliminate the sound of the so -called "anti -China Random Port". "

