#### Levi Strauss & Co (New York Stock Exchange code: Levi)

LEVI Strauss & CO, the old -fashioned denim clothing manufacturer LEVI Strauss, lowered the company's profit forecast for the company's entire year after July 6, and the company's stock price fell 7.7 % immediately on Friday. The performance report also fully reflects the rising cost caused by factors such as inflation, which has hit its profit margin, and the company is now in the dilemma of the decline in sales channel sales.

According to Levi Straus's second quarter performance report as of May 28 this year, the Group's turnover decreased by 9 % year -on -year to $ 1.34 billion, and the adjustment of each share was $ 0.04.

Levistraus' direct sales channels with high profit margins have achieved a 13 % increase in turnover in the second quarter. However, because wholesalers tighten the inventory of goods in North America and Europe, the company's wholesale channels have fallen by 22 %. On the whole, its American market sales fell 22 %, and the European market sales reduced by 2 %.

Refinitiv previously went online and offline for Levistrauss performance. The average prediction of analysts collected was a turnover of US $ 1.34 billion and a profit of $ 0.03 per share. Judging from the performance of this quarter, Levistrauss is barely reached. But the fatal injury of the stock is the prediction of its executive on the next performance.

These executives are now expected to make a profit from US $ 1.10 to $ 1.20 after this fiscal year, which is lower than the $ 1.30 to 1.40 US dollars they previously predicted. The adjusted gross profit margin is expected to decrease from 57.6 % of the last fiscal year, about 90 basis points, which is severe than the previously expected decrease of 50 basis points.

The executive of this clothing manufacturer also said that the Group's annual net turnover is expected to increase by 1.5 % to 2.5 % over the same period last year, and it has reduced the range of 1.5 % to 3 % of the previous forecast.

Levi Strauss CEO Chipbergh said at the online explanation meeting after the performance report was released: "The company will reduce the prices of about six products sold in retailers Macy's and Nordstrom, in order to attract more Consumers with more 'price sensitive'. "

![](Images/zaobao world/2023-07-10T20-01/000001.png)Levistrauss now attracts more consumers who are "price -sensitive". (File photo)

These products will include core denim products, such as Levi ’s 502 jeans that can be sold across seasons.

Perhaps because the retail industry is unclear, the eight analysts of Tipranks are also different. Four "buy" rating of Levistrauss shares, four given "holding" rating, the average target price of the one -year period is 16.75 Dollar.

